channel.title: Cannot connect!
channel.description: Hi, I was playing on this one server, but had to get off. Today, i wanted to play it again, but i couldn't get on. I had the IP, my user and pass all in. Was even on Hamachi. Can someone please tell me if i'm missing something here?
